  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Ministry of Justice statement in fee-paid judicial litigation: October 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A further update on work MOJ is doing to respond to the CJEU judgment of November 2018 in O’Brien No.2 and the Supreme Court’s judgment in Miller of December 2019.</p>

  </div>
</div>

