      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This update to the Employment Tribunal provides a further progress report on payments in lieu of pension (PILs) for eligible retired claimants in respect of their pre-7 April 2000 service. It also includes an updated template for the letter that is sent to PILs recipients, with improved information content and layout. In addition, we have provided data sheets setting out the fee rates we use in PILs calculations for years before 2000 to 2001 and data on average values for fee-paid sitting days.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

